4Geeks Academy offers a 16-week AI and Machine Learning bootcamp designed for beginners, aiming to prepare students for careers as data scientists without requiring prior experience. The curriculum covers essential tools and languages like Python, SQL, and statistics while focusing on creating predictive models using libraries such as Pandas and Numpy. Students will learn about both supervised and unsupervised learning, tackling real-world problems and AI projects end-to-end. Classes are conducted in small groups of up to 12 and available in English and Spanish. Graduates receive industry-recognized certificates. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop